-- Unicredit’s Vita Praises Merkel’s Euro Crisis Strategy, HB says
-- B y   A n n e t t e   W e i s b a c h
-- 2012-06-28T18:22:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-28/unicredit-s-vita-praises-merkel-s-euro-crisis-strategy-hb-says.html
Unicredit SpA Chairman Giuseppe Vita
said  Angela Merkel  is doing everything right in her fight
against the debt crisis, Handelsblatt reported, citing an
interview.  Unicredit will never need state funding even if the
difficult situation for the banking industry prevails,
Handelsblatt cited Vita as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
